	<text>
		<body>
			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original">
					<p>The original transcription is not available.</p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation">
					<pb facs="EHRI-DR-19440525-SK_01.jpg" n="1"/>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3054643/budapest.html">Budapest</placeName>, <date when="1944-05-25">May 25 1944</date></p>
					<p>Note: Confidential</p>
					<pb facs="EHRI-DR-19440525-SK_06.jpg" n="6"/>
					<p>The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-351" type="subject">Jewish Question</term> is being solved at a fast pace and with absolute precision. In the countryside, the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject"
							>Jews</term> are already <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-552" type="subject">concentrated</term> in <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545" type="subject">ghettos</term>. At the outskirts of <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/3054643/budapest.html">Budapest</placeName>, this is currently happening. The State Secretary <persName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000111">Endre Laszló</persName> who is responsible for the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jewish</term> issues told me that the separation of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> will be, in the end, also <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-625" type="subject">carried out</term> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3054643/budapest.html">Budapest</placeName>. In the area of two army-corps (<placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/724443/kosice.html">Kosice</placeName> and <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/681290/cluj-napoca.html">Kolozsvar</placeName>), the amount of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term>
						doubled, compared to the statistical data. From the <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html">German</placeName> circles I get the information that <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html"
							>Germany</placeName> should be <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">taking</term> about 300,000 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term>, daily conducting 12 full <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-522" type="subject">trains</term>. <persName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000111">Endre Laszló</persName> also told me that he is discussing the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-521" type="subject">transport</term> expenses with <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html">Germans</placeName>.</p>
					<p>(...)</p>
					<p>Delegate</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dr_spisiak_jan">Spišiak</persName></p>
